{
  "stem": "107.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was-- he had a laboratory in Vienna, so he knew enough medical terms to bluff, but he had never treated patients, but he had them see one position that was about equal to-- to Otto, who was an extremely decent person.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] At Yom Kippur in this year, so very soon after our arrival there, I experienced the first of these bad things that were called selections.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were two selections-- selections for-- of arriving people and to work for us, and people to be executed at the entrance.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then there was the other selection, which took time-- which took place time and again selecting people that were not active enough anymore to be of any worth, not in our camp.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Our camp was still 5,000 as we came in, but next door in the women's lager, frauenlager, took-- there was a selection on the evening of Yom Kippur of-- in '43.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Of course, I didn't-- I had heard rumors, but had no idea what it really is.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The first thing that happened that everybody has to go in other camps inside the barracks.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Nobody is allowed to look out or go out of the barrack.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I was very curious and went to the gate of our hospital barrack, and said, hospitals should have some privilege, and opened a little bit the gate to look out.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And what I saw were naked women in the women's lager thrown-- I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Thrown onto a car-- I mean, a truck.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So it seemed to me younger women-- I mean, at some distance.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were all naked, and they were really thrown, and with hands up in the air, and legs are spread out there, screamed [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Some Jewish religious--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH], I think it was, yeah.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
